        </div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-1000" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:h98bh6">
          About <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-slate-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:ftn430">TieBack</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-slate-400 font-light leading-relaxed animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-1000 delay-100" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7nd">
          Product identity for a more <span class="text-white font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:ftn42z">transparent</span> world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why TieBack Exists -->
  <section class="py-32 border-t border-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k5q">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fp">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fq">
        <div data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fr" class="scroll-reveal">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte8v">Why TieBack exists</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gd">
            <p data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7nc">Products have always carried stories.</p>
            <p class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#0080FF]/30" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7nb">
              Where they were made.<br/>
              What they are made from.<br/>
              How they should be used.<br/>
              Who stands behind them.
            </p>
            <p data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mp">
              For decades, that information lived on packaging, in manuals, or in fragmented systems. Most of it was discarded. Some of it was inaccessible. None of it was persistent.
            </p>
            <p data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mo">
              Digital Product Passport legislation did not create this problem. It acknowledged it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-white font-semibold pt-4" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mn">
              TieBack exists because physical products deserve structured, lasting digital identity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative group scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1ge">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[#0080FF]/10 rounded-3xl blur-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gf"></div>
          <img 
            crossorigin="anonymous"
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" 
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1744868562210-fffb7fa882d9?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
            sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw"
            alt="Server room datacenter infrastructure" 
            class="relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2ajx3b" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Shift -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-slate-950/50 relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k5r">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,rgba(0,128,255,0.02),transparent)]" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:shift-bg"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gg">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-20 scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gh">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte8w">The shift</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mm">Regulation is accelerating a broader transition.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gi">
        {[
          { title: "Transparency", desc: "Consumers expect it.", icon: "Eye" },
          { title: "Trust", desc: "Brands need it at scale.", icon: "Shield" },
          { title: "Traceability", desc: "Supply chains require it.", icon: "Network" },
          { title: "Visibility", desc: "Sustainability demands it.", icon: "Leaf" },
          { title: "Precision", desc: "Safety requires it.", icon: "Target" },
          { title: "Clarity", desc: "Our ultimate goal.", icon: "Sparkles" }
        ].map((item, i) => (
          <div 
            class="group p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 hover:border-[#0080FF] hover:bg-[#0080FF]/5 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_-15px_rgba(0,128,255,0.3)] transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-reveal"
            style={`transition-delay: ${i * 100}ms`}
            data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gj"
          >
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 bg-slate-800 text-[#0080FF] group-hover:bg-[#0080FF] group-hover:text-white group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:icon-box">
              <i data-lucide={item.icon} class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white group-hover:text-[#0080FF] transition-colors duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:c3liys">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7ml">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 text-center text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto italic" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gk">
        "Digital Product Passport formalises these expectations. But compliance alone is not the goal. The goal is clarity."
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our View -->
  <section class="py-24 border-y border-slate-900 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k5s">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1gm">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1h8">
          <img 
            crossorigin="anonymous"
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" 
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760435107992-f4714801666b?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
            sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw"
            alt="Digital infrastructure network" 
            class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2ajx3c" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1h9">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte8x">Our view</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mk">We believe every physical product should:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              "Carry a persistent digital identity",
              "Remain updateable over time",
              "Support authenticity and provenance",
              "Enable ownership continuity",
              "Surface safety information when it matters",
              "Connect brands and users beyond first sale"
            ].map(point => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:3bsaov">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#0080FF] mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                {point}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 text-slate-400" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1ha">
            Not through fragmented tools. <span class="text-white font-medium" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv0k">Through one structured layer.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compliance & Product as a Channel -->
  <section class="py-24 relative" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k6e">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hb">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hc">
        <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hd">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:c3liyr">Compliance, redesigned</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mj">Regulation often feels like a burden: Spreadsheets, manual validation, reactive audits.</p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 font-medium mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mi">We designed TieBack so compliance becomes structured infrastructure.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:3bsaow">• Validation activates when required</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:3bsaox">• Baseline data remains visible before mandates</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:3bsaoy">• Version history is preserved automatically</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0080FF]/5 border border-[#0080FF]/20" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1he">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:c3liyq">Product as a channel</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mh">The only thing that remains with a customer after purchase is the product itself.</p>
          <p class="text-white font-medium mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7mg">TieBack treats the product as a living digital endpoint.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hf">
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hg">Authenticity</div>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1hh">Product Data</div>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i3">Safety Guidance</div>
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i4">Aftercare</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust & Scale -->
  <section class="py-32 border-t border-slate-900 bg-slate-950/50" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k6f">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i5">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center mb-32" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i6">
        <div class="scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i7">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte9j">Trust without friction</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7lu">
            Trust should not introduce complexity. TieBack applies structured identity, anomaly detection, and optional higher-assurance verification behind the scenes.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i8">
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:border-[#0080FF]/40 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv16">No wallets</span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:border-[#0080FF]/40 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv17">No tokens</span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:border-[#0080FF]/40 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv18">Just Scan & Understand</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 scroll-reveal" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1i9">
          <div class="space-y-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1ia">
            <div class="group h-40 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center hover:border-[#0080FF]/30 transition-all duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1ib">
              <i data-lucide="file-check" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0080FF] mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
              <span class="text-white font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv19">DPP Align</span>
            </div>
            <div class="group h-56 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center hover:border-[#0080FF]/30 transition-all duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1ic">
              <i data-lucide="user-check" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0080FF] mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
              <span class="text-white font-bold px-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv1a">Ownership Continuity</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6 pt-12" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwk">
            <div class="group h-56 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center hover:border-[#0080FF]/30 transition-all duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwl">
              <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0080FF] mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
              <span class="text-white font-bold px-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv1b">Market Aware</span>
            </div>
            <div class="group h-40 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center hover:border-[#0080FF]/30 transition-all duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwm">
              <i data-lucide="bar-chart" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0080FF] mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></i>
              <span class="text-white font-bold" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:6ovv1c">Resale Visibility</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission Statement -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/30 p-12 md:p-24 rounded-[4rem] relative overflow-hidden scroll-reveal shadow-[0_0_80px_-20px_rgba(0,128,255,0.1)]" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwn">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(0,128,255,0.05),transparent_70%)]" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwo"></div>
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#0080FF] mb-8" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte9k">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white leading-tight relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7lt">
          To give every physical product a structured digital identity — so transparency, trust, and lifecycle continuity become the standard, not the exception.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-32 border-t border-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k6g">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwp">
      <div class="bg-[#0080FF] rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-20 relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwq">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwr"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtws">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:2kte9l">Request access</h2>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7ls">
            If TieBack fits your product and rollout goals, request access and we'll guide onboarding through first setup to launch readiness.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:txwtwt">
            <a href="/request-access" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#0080FF] font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-black/10" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:691p1n">
              Request access
            </a>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm italic italic" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:uw7lr">
              Access is released in carefully selected cohorts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <script>
    import { createIcons, Eye, ShieldCheck, Network, Leaf, Target, Sparkles, Box, Repeat, Globe, TrendingUp, Shield, FileCheck, UserCheck, BarChart } from 'lucide';

    // Initialize Lucide icons - Ensure all used icons are registered
    createIcons({
      icons: { 
        Eye, 
        ShieldCheck, 
        Network, 
        Leaf, 
        Target, 
        Sparkles, 
        Box, 
        Repeat, 
        Globe, 
        TrendingUp,
        Shield,
        FileCheck,
        UserCheck,
        BarChart
      }
    });

    // Intersection Observer for scroll animations
    const observerOptions = {
      root: null,
      rootMargin: '0px',
      threshold: 0.1
    };

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('active');
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    document.querySelectorAll('.scroll-reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

  <style>
    .scroll-reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    
    .scroll-reveal.active {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .scroll-reveal:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 100ms; }
    .scroll-reveal:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 200ms; }
    .scroll-reveal:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 300ms; }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>

---
import BaseLayout from &#x27;@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro&#x27;;


<BaseLayout
  title="About — TieBack"
  description="Why TieBack exists: structured digital identity for physical products, designed for transparency, trust, and Digital Product Passport readiness."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-40 pb-32 overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:518k5p">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fl">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(0,128,255,0.08),transparent_50%)]" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fm"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#0080FF]/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-pulse" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fm-pulse"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fn">
      <div class="max-w-3xl" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:4st1fo">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#0080FF]/10 border border-[#0080FF]/20 text-[#0080FF] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-700" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:badge">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:ftn433">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#0080FF] opacity-75" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:ftn432"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[#0080FF]" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:ftn431"></span>
          </span>
          Infrastructure d&#x27;identité
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-1000" data-ps="src/pages/about.astro:h98bh6">
        
